OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe scattered to frequent blustery
OL,7,Fshowers feeding in from the northwest
OL,8,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,9,Fthese showers may be heavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool and
OL,12,Fblustery with bright or sunny spells
OL,13,Fand scattered showers, these heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
