OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FQuite
OL,6,Fcloudy with some showers or longer
OL,7,Fspells of rain on Thursday, becoming
OL,8,Fdrier later. Largely dry, bright
OL,9,FFriday with variable cloud. Dry,
OL,10,Fbright start Saturday, then rain
OL,11,Fspreading east.
